      .inner
        p Here you can download Queen's Awards for Enterprise resources for use in your websites and advertising materials. The Winners' Manual provides more detailed information on where and how you are allowed to use these resources.

        br

        h2 Download The Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners' Manual 2016

        .form-download
          p
            = link_to "Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners' Manual 2016 (PDF, 1.4MB)",
                      static_s3_asset_path(2016, "Queen's Awards for Enterprise Winners Manual 2016.pdf"),
                      class: "thumbnail",
                      target: "_blank"

          p
            ' Please do not publicise the information in the press book until
            strong
              => deadline_for("buckingham_palace_attendees_details", "%d %B")
